          "answerGuidance": [
            "400 kV",
            "400kV"
          ],
          "hint": "It is the largest of the three standard transmission voltages.",
          "sourceTeachingPointIds": [
            "TP1",
            "TP3"
          ]
        },
        {
          "questionText": "What does the 'k' represent in the unit kV?",
          "answerGuidance": [
            "Kilo",
            "1,000",
            "One thousand"
